Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.81,0:02:09.81,op-en,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}You think we're different
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.81,0:02:12.69,op-en,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}You think we never feel the way you do
